snippet.textDisplay: I think the message of this video is that Abel and that girl used to be together but he broke things off with the girl.  But now that he’s come to realization that he likes her again and he can’t live with out her, he becomes crazy so he goes to look for her but he finds out that she already found someone new. So he kills her new lover and tries to get her back but she is seen running away because she might not want him back after he’s hurt her. So in the end after she kills Abel and keeps his head is almost like a token to her because it shows that he’ll never leave her again. And we see him not fighting back because he’s giving in to her just so that they could be together. That’s what I personally think based of the Album’s  lyrics. If I’m wrong feel free to correct me
